messages.message: Defining AJAX using $GLOBALS['TYPO3_CONF_VARS']['BE']['AJAX'][$ajaxID] is no longer supported with a single String like 'something'. Since TYPO3 7.6, use PSR-7-based Routing for Backend AJAX Requests. See: https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/core/7.6/Changelog/7.6/Feature-69916-PSR-7-basedRoutingForBackendAJAXRequests.html

Defining AJAX using $GLOBALS['TYPO3_CONF_VARS']['BE']['AJAX'][$ajaxID] is no longer supported with a single String like "something". Since TYPO3 7.6, use PSR-7-based Routing for Backend AJAX Requests. See: https://docs.typo3.org/typo3cms/extensions/core/7.6/Changelog/7.6/Feature-69916-PSR-7-basedRoutingForBackendAJAXRequests.html
